---
title: Easy Creamy Tomato & Chorizo Fettuccine with Rocket & Parmesan Salad
description: Golden strands of fettuccine combine with rich tomato paste, cream and smokey chorizo to create an elegant meal fit for only the
best. Add sharp Parmesan and a rocket salad for crunch and dinner is complete.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/easy-creamy-tomato-chorizo-fettuccine-426f741d.jpg
